Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.64,0:23:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}呢喃細語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}你的夢想將會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:23:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}轉動命運的車輪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.33,0:24:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}我總是感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.77,0:24:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}自己並不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.09,0:24:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}直到發現那瞳孔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.45,0:24:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}在內心的某個角落裡閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.46,0:24:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}就彷彿高懸的明月只有一輪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.55,0:24:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}所有崎嶇的小路
